  "keyFeatures": [
    "Master/Wrapper cluster topology with Hazelcast-based task dispatch",
    "Template-based instance deployment with dynamic variable replacement",
    "Pluggable runtimes: screen, tmux, Docker, and Kubernetes",
    "S3-backed remote template storage for multi-node setups",
    "Tailscale mesh-network IP template variables for cross-node connectivity",
    "Full REST API + interactive WebSocket console",
    "Extension system for custom runtimes, storage, metrics, and integrations",
    "GitOps and ArgoCD integration for declarative configuration management",
    "First-class Minecraft platform support (Paper, Spigot, Velocity, BungeeCord, Folia)",
    "Single fat JAR deployment — Master and Wrapper from the same artifact",
    "Port conflict prevention via three-source port allocation strategy",
    "Prometheus and InfluxDB metrics export extensions"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
